  "text": "Stochastic decoding was proposed in [CITATION_1] for the binary case, then extended to non-binary LDPC codes in [CITATION_2] . Using the same message names as in Fig. 1 , but noting that here a message is no longer a pmf, but rather a symbol, the algorithm can be described as follows:",
